{"tid":2151443,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果25 週年 《不是最終章》","createTime":"2020-08-11T11:36:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T16:35:09.000Z","uid":237487,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"d738f3cfa9c8d180cebc875ee481a86201f22d4e","tid":2151443,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T11:36:17.000Z","msg":"轉述：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QUX4osS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQUX4osS.jpg&h=6bb05af5&s={SIZE}\" />【支持壹傳媒集團=支持新聞自由】<br />\n<br />\n我係一位普通香港市民。<br />\n而家父係一名報販。<br />\n<br />\n有一個盲點係普通市民未必會知，大部份報章雜誌賣唔出係會退回俾發行商。<br />\n<br />\n而蘋果日報早前出版左一本《不是最終章》，由於疫情影響，大部份關注點都轉移到抗疫上，導致呢本書賣得好差好差，一個月只賣出兩三本，而每個報攤都有40, 50本。<br />\n<br />\n今日家父通知我，仲有不足十日，呢本《不是最終章》就要退回比蘋果。<br />\n該書籍零售定價$99，若然全數退回，只會令其變成廢紙。<br />\n<br />\n各位除左支持買報紙、訂閱之外。<br />\n順手買埋《不是最終章》好嗎？<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源：￼網絡<br />\n文章來源：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/westerndistrict/permalink/10157097802735286/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fwesterndistrict%2Fpermalink%2F10157097802735286%2F&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FhVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=08fd1044\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/westerndistrict/permalink/10157097802735286/</a>"},{"pid":"86a526bc1870e73e4e82566b14729118ea963361","tid":2151443,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T11:36:44.000Z","msg":"我自己今日都見到呢本野幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知咩嚟"},{"pid":"e7ed6002682b5aa25e9e725f03eab406c9299824","tid":2151443,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T11:37:10.000Z","msg":"等陣落去再買先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f76f7301a24d09f72f231958cb71e61cb031451d","tid":2151443,"uid":110851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T11:42:10.000Z","msg":"見唔到 已經賣晒<img sr